Repeating is difficult, but not impossible.  Since 1990, there have been 10 repeats, including the Bulls two threepeats and one Laker threepeat.  Giannis is young and playing as well as he did last season.  The Bucks will have an easier path to the finals than Golden State.

Bucks, Suns and Jazz are all looking really great with solid teams and records so far. Nets team doesn't look as good as the other three, but have a good record. Warriors are performing better than expected at the beginning of the season. Preference to the Bucks because they won last year and they're the local team to me.
